author: Legonater
title: If only if only...
review:
Sadly, this is the only Res Q set I didn't get, since it ws a promotional. But it seems amasing. Though the truck is strange, the life post is just increadable, and includes a pony tail piece I still don't have.
If only I got this set...

author: J_tje
title: Strange Combo
review:
Another nice little set in the Res-Q series. I find the Beachguard a great idea (and nicely done), but I find the vehicle a bit boring (and strange to include in this beach set). it would have made more sense in my opinion if this set had the Jetski set from this series instead of this car that does not seem to have any (special) capabilities.

 

Nice minifig's especialy the female and good playability, a great addition to any towns beach scene.
